"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**本次消息来源**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kcsVZVBhsDxSaxqBiKtRB.png?height=309&width=629)\\n\\n**「1」下载xtz钱包：Temple（过程略过，记好密码，助记词）\\n下载链接：**\\n\\n[https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/temple-tezos-wallet-ex-th/ookjlbkiijinhpmnjffcofjonbfbgaoc](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/temple-tezos-wallet-ex-th/ookjlbkiijinhpmnjffcofjonbfbgaoc)\\n\\n**「2」Tezos域名注册网站**\\n\\n[https://app.tezos.domains/](https://app.tezos.domains/)\\n\\n**「3」链接钱包**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JsJ3IGUQ_RAgIbXQQRKDZ.png?height=788&width=1479)\\n\\n**「4」搜索自己想拥有的Web3.0域名**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2DFXjV95kmPSmgAokcB0B.png?height=451&width=1021)\\n\\n** \\n 「5」从交易所转出XTZ（钱包显示代币名称TEZ，其实就是XTZ，如需选择主网，要选择Tezos主网）**\\n\\n**「6」对想要的域名发出购买请求**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/GsTYSjsG3oK62d4mXjr8q.png?height=493&width=1036)\\n\\n**「7」选择购买期限（建议5-10年以上）（确保域名指向是自己的Tezos钱包地址）**\",\"timestamp\":1640953295,\"title\":\"Tezos上域名注册（.tez）（空投教程）\"},\"digest\":\"XF_NuLdZJ1zjLE6RCHbnCETaSE8I8EAsu9vFh3DGMMo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x7Ae8ED015d2Ceb12f194aFB4284279Df791A99E9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mRM6bvBmZ0VkdTamaEfiq1b3CCujkzzJKx6QUcD0rEs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FsaCIXtjWdlrT1BTbCzL4Bv09HqOFHD4hcqKMxvy2AU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"8EfA6HRT8YcPOCOz2ZEVp2OJ19HfcOiSjf7OqZzki6Q3blhBzeeZo2URHG2LIP9w50hEj4zgE9hzITcsMXGuHw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa94cb1b484c796eb8cfc44640e595359d3973eade4196fd0819dbbf39e9ac1f1156cd8430381742b6e0485edf747fb6e4060ed6c688f334983e9b7a28250a8cc1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"mRM6bvBmZ0VkdTamaEfiq1b3CCujkzzJKx6QUcD0rEs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"FsaCIXtjWdlrT1BTbC